  • Classes in seng201.islandtradergame.core used by seng201.islandtradergame.core
    Class Description
    Island
    This class implements an Island that can be travelled to, this island has its own store an posible routes to get here from other islands.
    Item
    This class implements an Item which can be bought and sold at the other islands in exchange for money.
    Route
    This class implements a Route which specifies the route from one island to another.
    Ship
    This class implements a Ship which contains the traders bought items and can have have more capacity and travel faster depending on the ship created.
    Store
    This class implements a Store which specifies the items that can be bought and sold by the trader.
